### Register a Household User
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "household@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "role": "HOUSEHOLD",
  "phone": "+1234567890"
}

### Register a Worker
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "plumber@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "John Plumber",
  "role": "WORKER",
  "phone": "+1987654321",
  "skills": ["plumbing", "drain cleaning"]
}

### Register a Vendor
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vendor@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Vince Veggies",
  "role": "VENDOR",
  "phone": "+1555555555",
  "businessName": "Vince's Fresh Market"
}

### Log In
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "household@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}
